description:
It's been a long time since I wanted to do a session of this kind, taking the best of the bootlegs made by the Reflex and the DJs, two names that I really appreciate and that I feel true lords of old style. I did not settle down with the times and in the end I realized it was 5 hours long but slipped that it is a beauty! I hope you will appreciate the project, merit is not logically my own but their wonderful versions!
Thank you for having been in all these years for your comments, downloads and listening, but it is time to go, who knows, maybe one day we will meet again!
We come in peace... always!
